      "unit_id": "799fafdeeb6ed59da377bd1f45409792192bf626e246fa72d999bb9fec683fe2"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "董事会决议建议就截至",
      "unit_id": "37146c46e9ee66450aaf98e9299052dd2eff6e185e85c54e4fdfaccaad2ece64"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "年度每股派发末期股息人民币0.0111元（含税），合共净额为人民币9,966,024元予",
      "unit_id": "22405e8a55bd2c0a936a5b6a258a3931549587a577727870efaf770d376268b1"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "于2026年6月5日（星期五）名列本公司",
      "unit_id": "dd244f2476d8ae4515c0364e80330370263cfdf7cc971d9d56853470fffb03f0"
    },
    {
