      "unit_id": "e75ce5f0542b8193f5cb2e348304960a64abfd2196fa3fede4ff1bb1bd2dc3f8"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "股东，惟须待",
      "unit_id": "ba33623b15561b9937b0dbfb79fbbff6e0f616064565d5fdde312342b2a9d92b"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "股东于2026年5月28日（星期四）举行的即将召开的",
      "unit_id": "e480a78d7ec823da552ee74d0c59f352b261c7c8a5a0e7d3757ecd775f09badf"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "股东周年大会上批准。待",
      "unit_id": "98bb9fd6ef6252f5c6b0787fd51297cfdb78e7061296ee7cc536479df9263e0c"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "股东周年大会通过相关决议后，2025年",
      "unit_id": "15f624e838e8c481e58f51629423c557f309b9afc34aadcf271e103a25b68d02"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "末期股息预期将于2026年7月21日或前后派付。",
      "unit_id": "af99133ecfc59faeae60944a9e821b31295da3db00243b77623e90a89f3ccad2"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "本公司已采纳一项股息政策（“",
      "unit_id": "ff6d5307679fa1495b9913305c6146439faf64e6b892e3610e01c7cb57002358"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "），据此本公司可向",
      "unit_id": "be0f996b36d3f54cbb042e9d4f9691091d48baf1ccef1d8ecc65fc9239956a8b"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "股东宣派及派付股息。任何决定",
      "unit_id": "585b4ce5af6800924ba8776f1a709f7bf0931f0fda29e19a0f67e2a466a8c16f"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "宣派及派付股息须经",
      "unit_id": "d7c22e0525e57268ad8dace2890eb933f9d70823fb3f7430afc9c6a058e02fbf"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "董事会批准，并由其酌情决定。此外，任何",
      "unit_id": "e6bae90c1e413887e0f53d5a92a69f5336afa13f1fc72a25130fd2c948439313"
    },
    {
