      "unit_id": "3aadc233e6ad4eb9fbe442c30b0daa69f329d28142d6b4e39e3c9151a744f8f8"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "股东批准。董事会将根据我们的经营业绩、",
      "unit_id": "cff662b49c87bcbb31b1473d9c70055045ead95ae649afc068ae308bbc74a326"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "现金流、财务状况、",
      "unit_id": "e11e3930b95d5a2122b7fef7940aa30984e1df3363517e2731fc2183bd4be9a9"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "股东利益、资本",
      "unit_id": "cdd89527b88c6ead897fe6ed6258e3b0956d41675fff4a5ade533f09bd277db4"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "需求、一般业务状况及策略、",
      "unit_id": "474595bafb26991876d2e425110d7ead562562acd2ece13982aa00f1c082b1cf"
    },
    {
      "translated_text": "我们的附属公司向我们的现金股息派付，以及",
      "unit_id": "959f43f00fc4af59184c8ba9440eeb5b0277d98af59b18752ede3038e7c3d41a"
    },
    {
